<section class="learn-more">
  <div class="hero-banner">
    <div class="hero-banner-content">
      <h1 class="text-white">Learn More</h1>
      <p>Explore our features and services.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center mt-4">
    <div class="col-8">
      <p class="text-secondary">
        At <%= memories.site_name %>, we strive to offer the best experience in
        finding your ideal vehicle. Our platform provides comprehensive details
        on a wide range of cars, from the latest models to classic favorites.
        Here what you can expect when you explore our site:
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="container p-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h3 class="fw-bold">Extensive Car Database</h3>
        <p>
          We offer a vast database of car specifications, including detailed
          information on various makes, models, and generations. Whether you’re
          searching for a new or used car, our detailed listings help you make
          informed decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h3 class="fw-bold">Advanced Search Tools</h3>
        <p>
          Use our advanced search filters to narrow down your options based on
          brand, model, engine type, and more. Our intuitive search tools make
          it easy to find exactly what you're looking for, saving you time and
          effort.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h3 class="fw-bold">Real-Time Updates</h3>
        <p>
          Stay up-to-date with the latest car arrivals and specifications. Our
          platform provides real-time updates on new models, so you never miss
          out on the latest innovations and trends in the automotive industry.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-light p-5">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="fw-bold">Why Choose Us?</h2>
      <p class="text-secondary" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 20px auto">
        Our mission is to simplify your car search process by providing
        accurate, detailed, and up-to-date information. With user-friendly
        features and a dedicated support team, we’re here to assist you every
        step of the way in finding your dream car.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact-us" class="theme-btn">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container p-5">
    <h2 class="text-center fw-bold">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h4>How can I search for a car?</h4>
        <p>
          Simply use our search form available on the homepage or the search
          results page. You can filter by brand, model, engine type, and more to
          find cars that match your preferences.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h4>Do you provide financing options?</h4>
        <p>
          While we don't provide financing directly, we partner with several
          financial institutions that can assist you with car loans and
          financing options. Contact us for more details.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h4>Can I get alerts for new arrivals?</h4>
        <p>
          Yes! You can sign up for email notifications to receive updates on new
          car arrivals and special offers. Stay informed about the latest models
          and promotions by subscribing to our newsletter.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h4>How do I contact customer support?</h4>
        <p>
          Our customer support team is available via email or phone. Visit our
          contact page for more details on how to get in touch with us for any
          questions or assistance you may need.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</section>
